        <abstract> 
<p>Russian translation of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi> in progress, but the Minister of Interior has banned CD’s work and the book will be seized.</p> 
            <p>His foolish brother-in-law, Mayor of Montmartre, attempted to defend their section against the government.</p>
            <p>CD’s queries on man and camels have gone to Alexander [Kovalevsky] in Sinai.</p>
        </abstract>
